maintext:
SPRINGFIELD, Ill. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Saturday afternoon’s drawing of the Illinois Lottery’s “LuckyDay Lotto Midday” game were:
07-18-29-40-42
(seven, eighteen, twenty-nine, forty, forty-two)
